high_descs: Walk toward the bathroom sink and turn to face it
Pick up the green sponge from the counter
Approach the sink and drop the green sponge in it
Turn on the sink and run water, then turn it off
Turn around and approach the bath tub
Drop the green sponge into the bath tub
anns.task_desc: Pick up the green sponge from the bathroom counter and place it into the bath tub

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the sink.
Pick up the sponge to the right of the sink.
Take a step to the left.
Wash the sponge in the sink.
Turn around and walk to the bath tub.
Place the sponge in the bath tub.
anns.task_desc: Place a sponge in the bathtub.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the sink on the left.
Pick up the sponge from the counter top to the right of the sink.
Walk slightly left to the sink.
Put the sponge in the sink, rinse it off, and take it out of the sink.
Turn around and walk forward to the bath tub.
Put the sponge in the bath tub basin.
anns.task_desc: Put a cleaned sponge in a bath tub.

high_descs: Turn and go to the bathroom counter to the right of the sink.
Pick up the sponge that is to the right of the sink.
Take the sponge with you and move so you are in front of the sink.
Place the sponge to the right of the soap that is in the sink.  Turn the water on to get the sponge wet.  Turn the water off and pick up the sponge.
With the sponge in hand move to the bath tub.
Place the sponge in the center of the bath tub.
anns.task_desc: Wet a sponge to put in bath tub.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the white door, then hang left and go to the bathroom vanity.
Grab the green sponge on the vanity counter.
Go to the sink on your left.
Put the sponge in the sink, wash it with water, and then grab it again.
Turn around and walk to the bath tub.
Put the sponge in the bath tub.
anns.task_desc: Wash the sponge and put it in the bath tub.

high_descs: go to the counter to the right of the sink
pick up the green sponge from the counter
take the sponge over to the sink
clean the sponge in the sink with the soap
walk the clean sponge over to the tub basin
stand the sponge up on it's end in the tub
anns.task_desc: get a sponge from the counter, wash it, then put it in the tub
